HEADWORD: evaporated
<hw>evaporated</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>reduced in volume by having
moisture expelled before canning; same as <er>condensed</er>, 3; <as>as,
unsweetened <ex>evaporated</ex> milk</as>.</def>
